ble to choose the date and the time format Being able to sort the feed items by title (instead of the default date/time) Some changes and bug fixes: &#8220;Link to author&#8221; in widget form becomes &#8220;Link to the [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="http://stefictservices.com/rss-just-better-plugin-version-0-8-released/">RSS Just Better Plugin version 0.8 released</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="http://stefictservices.com">Stef ICT Services</a>.</p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:4:"Stef";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1736:"<p>This version includes a few new features:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Being able to truncate/limit the title to (given) chars</li>\n<li>Being able to choose the date and the time format</li>\n<li>Being able to sort the feed items by title (instead of the default date/time)</li>\n</ul>\n<div>Some changes and bug fixes:</div>\n<ul>\n<li>&#8220;Link to author&#8221; in widget form becomes &#8220;Link to the Plugin Homepage&#8221;</li>\n<li>The popup window showing on mouseover title is limited to 400 char</li>\n<li>Optimized function to retrieve feed and format list</li>\n<li>Changed error message when feed URL does not return the items list:  if it has already worked before, it must be just a feed temporary issue and not a misformatted feed</li>\n<li>Fixed the plugin homepage URI in the readme.txt file</li>\n</ul>\n<div>Pages on <a href="http://stefictservices.com/rss-just-better-plugin-for-wordpress/rss-just-better-usage-sample/">how to use it</a> and better <a href="http://stefictservices.com/rss-just-better-plugin-for-wordpress/demo-rss-just-better-plugin/">demo</a> have also been added to this blog.</div>\n<p>Now,  for the users who wait for the ability to read and display images within the feed, please be patient it&#8217; s a major change and I&#8217;m still working/thinking about it.</p>\n<p>Any comment or remark please drop me a live via the contact form.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="http://stefictservices.com/rss-just-better-plugin-version-0-8-released/">RSS Just Better Plugin version 0.8 released</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="http://stefictservices.com">Stef ICT Services</a>.</p>\n<img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/StefaniasBlog/~4/5aWM5U2tvGk" height="1" width="1" alt=""/>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:76:"http://stefictservices.com/rss-just-better-plugin-version-0-8-released/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:42:"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0";a:1:{s:8:"origLink";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:71:"http://stefictservices.com/rss-just-better-plugin-version-0-8-released/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:9;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:39:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:6:{s:0:"";a:6:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:43:"RSS Just Better Plugin version 0.7 released";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:60:"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/StefaniasBlog/~3/O1nbi-oYCkg/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17: